      <title>[筆記] inxi 蒐集詳盡的硬體資訊 / inxi Collect Detail Hardware Info</title>
      <link>https://blog.cowbay.org/p/%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98-inxi-%E8%92%90%E9%9B%86%E8%A9%B3%E7%9B%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AC%E9%AB%94%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A-/-inxi-collect-detail-hardware-info/</link>
